`4++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++``
`8Keywords``   : Cry
`8Categories`` : 
`4++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++``

`8Syntax:`` 

 * cast cry <target>

 This is the use of one's will to change the emotions of the target.  Quite
simply, it makes them cry.  This emotional outburst causes a temporary loss of
strength and dexterity.  The amount of that loss is dependent on the level of
the caster.

`4++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++``
